Program: Omnibus
Title: My Father's Island
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376mg4
Last Broadcast Date: 08 August 2002
The story of the Angermeyer brothers who sailed to the Galapagos Islands from Germany in 1937 to escape the coming war in Europe. Johanna Angermeyer recounts the story of their adventures and the father she never met.